main event: A round light object was observed in the sky over Orlando, Florida for 30-45 minutes.
interesting points: The object changed color from red to yellow-orange to white.
The object moved like a gyroscope and left a vapor trail when it disappeared.
The object appeared to move erratically, rapidly changing altitudes while moving from south to west.
The object was observed by multiple witnesses over a total time of 25-30 minutes.
A color sketch of the object was provided to the interviewer, but insufficient data was available to identify the object.
witnesses: multiple witnesses, including a student and military personnel
